  <brief_title>The Effects of Intraoperative Dexmedetomidine Infusion on Postoperative Bowel Movement in Patients Undergoing Laparoscopic Gastrectomy</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Yonsei University</agency>
