        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  ASA physical status Ⅳ

          -  bradycardia (&lt; 60 bpm), arrhythmia

          -  uncompensated heart failure

          -  hepatic failure (Child-Pugh score B 이상)

          -  renal failure (eGFR MDRD &lt; 60 ml/min/1.73m2)
